        {
            "title": "美股日誌｜納指大跌2%　老麥可樂創新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美股日誌｜納指大跌2% 老麥可樂創新高\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RcxQoOmYfJ_IPV84uo0u5w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/dc346560-0860-11f1-9d7c-b43ec6542e78\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美股日誌｜納指大跌2% 老麥可樂創新高</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國股市周四急挫，道指下跌約1.3%，即逾660點，標普500指數下跌1.6%，納指跌幅最大，下挫超過2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">黃金期貨下跌3%，比特幣亦回落至約65,000美元水平，跌幅同樣逾3%，顯示投資者風險胃納下降，投資者關注明天公布的消費物價指數數據，以尋找對減息前景有否線索。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場正憂慮哪些行業最易受到人工智能顛覆的影響，科技股普遍下跌，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:思科;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CSCO/\">思科</a>股價下跌超過 12%，而<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Meta;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/META/\">Meta</a>、<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Amazon;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/AMZN/\">Amazon</a>及<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:蘋果;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/AAPL/\">蘋果</a>均大幅回落，其中蘋果下跌約 5%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-48015999-0afd-427b-bdd3-2dc7d76ef9aa-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_article_&amp;af_sub1=Acquisition&amp;af_sub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_&amp;uuid=eDFkEhESdIhPGYRE2850\"><ins>下載Yahoo財經APP</ins></a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2月12日（星期四）市况</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:道瓊斯指數;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EDJI\"> <ins>道瓊斯指數</ins></a> 跌669.92點或1.34%，報49,451.98點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:標普500指數;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EGSPC\"> <ins>標普500指數</ins></a> 跌108.71點或1.57%，報6,832.76點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:8;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:納斯達克指數;cpos:8;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EIXIC\"> <ins>納斯達克指數</ins></a> 跌469.32點或2.03%，報22,597.15點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:9;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約3月期油;cpos:9;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CL=F\"> <ins>紐約3月期油</ins></a> 收報62.91美元一桶，跌1.72美元或2.66%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:10;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期金;cpos:10;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/GC=F\"> <ins>紐約4月期金</ins></a> 收報4,937.5美元一盎司，跌161美元或3.16%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:11;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:比特幣;cpos:11;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC-USD/\"> <ins>比特幣</ins></a> 截至美東時間下午4時報65,338.66美元, 跌2,184.76美元或3.23%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:12;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:美國10年期國債息率;cpos:12;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5ETNX\"> <ins>美國10年期國債息率</ins></a> 收報4.104厘。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">路透社引述消息人士報道，在中美兩國元首4月會晤之前，特朗普政府將擱置一系列針對北京的關鍵技術安全措施，這些措施包括禁止中國電信（728）在美國開展業務，以及限制向美國數據中心出售中國設備，似乎有意製造有利會議的環境。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國全國房地產經紀人協會(NAR)數據顯示，美國現有住宅銷售在今年1月按月下降8.4%，年化銷售率降至391萬套，遠低於市場預期的418萬套。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">科技股無運行，業績亮麗的傳統股成為逆市奇葩。餐飲股<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:13;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:麥當勞;cpos:13;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/MCD/\">麥當勞</a>在美國銷售額於第四季度實現兩年多以來的最快增長，季度營收達70億美元，同比增長9.5%，超出預期1.6億美元。股價收市升2.7%，創歷史新高。<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:14;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:可口可樂;cpos:14;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/KO/\">可口可樂</a>業績後繼續強勢，同樣再創歷史新高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">洞洞鞋<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:15;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Crocs;cpos:15;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CROX/\">Crocs</a>公布業績，在新產品提振需下，去年第四季淨利潤1.05億美元，經調整每股盈利2.29美元，遠高於市場預期的1.91美元。公司對本季盈測亦勝預期，刺激股價急升，收市升19%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由軟銀集團支持的日本QR碼支付巨頭PayPay，計劃下月在美國納斯達克交易所上市。知情人士透露，公司的市值預計將超過3兆日圓(約196億美元)。軟銀計劃出售約10%的股份。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E6%97%A5%E8%AA%8C%EF%BD%9C%E7%B4%8D%E6%8C%87%E5%A4%A7%E8%B7%8C2-%E8%80%81%E9%BA%A5%E5%8F%AF%E6%A8%82%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-222507237.html",
