        {
            "title": "〈貴金屬盤後〉美國就業數據打壓降息預期 金價重挫近3%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bOtWAQ7rvmBIJ6hAiNCD2A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/d4d59484fb843d974b6e63fc5389719b\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%B4%E9%87%91%E5%B1%AC%E7%9B%A4%E5%BE%8C-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F-%E9%87%91%E5%83%B9%E9%87%8D%E6%8C%AB%E8%BF%913-211926569.html",
